{"tid":817190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以教我點溝呢條女","createTime":"2018-09-13T08:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T04:00:29.000Z","uid":122781,"like":1,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e5bd32efaa8a86574860e2e56df45a1c75961a5c","tid":817190,"uid":122781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"同個女仔whatsApp傾左2個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係傾左1個月左右我想約佢出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話同我未熟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熟啲先 咁前幾日再話想約佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢同我講 你唔會約到我架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後再問佢已經轉移話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傾左呢2個月 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span> 覺得都幾了解到對方 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋傾得都算密 佢有時又會開話題好似想繼續同我傾落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實佢係咪只係當我網友咁樣？</span></span><br />\n係咪真係無機會約到佢同佢試下發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa20c507a3981f61d22545ea53edf71a6303c3a3","tid":817190,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"點識先"},{"pid":"597a92a18d655aeabda692e69b131e8aafb916aa","tid":817190,"uid":2419,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"唔係呀 佢拒絕你係想試下你誠意<br />\n狂約啦 佢唔覆你就打電話炸佢"},{"pid":"dc50751bfe1982a259aa713a98a8f49d1cc226bb","tid":817190,"uid":107472,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"一切都只係你覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426